summary:
Advanced Life Support Paramedic with fourteen years’ remote site experience in Afghanistan, Democratic Republic of the Congo, Madagascar, Ethiopia, Eritrea, Guinea, Kenya, Gabon, Liberia, Iraq, Western Sahara, Mali, Somaliland and offshore.  More than four years voluntary ALS Paramedic / Fire Fighter experience in high density areas of Johannesburg, South Africa.
HSE experience in Mining (Operations & Life Support) and Oil and Gas Industry (Life Support).
More than 15 years’ mining experience (production, projects and planning) in South Africa, Tanzania, Guinea and Mali in both underground- and surface mining before changing career to paramedic.
